snippet.title: The Magnet - Second Night
snippet.description:
This si the trailer for the game "The magnet - second night" . The magnet follows Teddie a young girl who is trying to survive the apocalypse. In this episode Teddie finally meets the visitor, that was teased in the last episode. 

The game is out now on itch.io and Newgrounds.com.
